{"tid":2312764,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"今日俾個死新丁韓妹同事蝦==","createTime":"2020-12-05T08:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T02:28:05.000Z","uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3711b423f1ce7551bdb2db39ef4f8a77296f4a8","tid":2312764,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"今朝開工之前老細帶佢嚟我哋條team度交代完幾句就走左<br />\n一開始我見佢Asian樣少似yuna<br />\n所以問咗佢一句你識唔識中文<br />\n之後佢答I don't know Chinese<br />\n諗住佢應該係普通唔識中文既ABC妹<br />\n後尾全日都同佢講英文<br />\n點知就快收工嗰陣拎部電話出嚟睇一睇時間<br />\n俾佢去偷睇到我wallpaper係周周之後<br />\n佢就突然爆韓文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />아이즈원  김민추시??<br />\n我聽到就嚇到窒咗一窒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一輪嘴講咗兩句唔知乜韓文之後就話<br />\nOhhh i see u real into IZONE hmmm~<br />\n<br />\n之後我就連收工交帶啲嘢都冇講<br />\n直接唔理佢跑去停車場返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260b0bf3e6b383117f966c44363aac298a91acf8","tid":2312764,"uid":373363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"1ae266badbeb0bc8a0c4779f9f23118100e178a7","tid":2312764,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />名都打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a8c1fbc19a544ded9ddd3c36bbc7f16a176bc7","tid":2312764,"uid":206810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"-10/10"},{"pid":"fc1ef6a4805e8ebc885d3ee9d87479c5815a6730","tid":2312764,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ae266badbeb0bc8a0c4779f9f23118100e178a7","tid":2312764,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />名都打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy